Os comandos a serem enviados para Cisco IOS são:

router bgp 100
neighbor 12.12.12.1 remote-as 200
network 192.168.200.0 mask 255.255.255.0
network 12.12.12.0 mask 255.255.255.0
network 1.1.1.0 mask 255.255.255.0

Para JunOS são:

set routing-options router-id 2.2.2.2
set routing-options autonomous-system 200
set protocols bgp group EXTERNAL-PEERS type external
set protocols bgp group EXTERNAL-PEERS local-address 12.12.12.2
set protocols bgp group EXTERNAL-PEERS export send-direct
set protocols bgp group EXTERNAL-PEERS neighbor 12.12.12.1 peer-as 100
set policy-options policy-statement send-direct term2 from protocol direct
set policy-options policy-statement send-direct term2 then accept
